dapps.name: Axie Infinity
dapps.description: Axie Infinity is a game about collecting and raising fantasy creatures called Axie, on the Ethereum platform.

dapps.name: Cent
dapps.description: Give wisdom, get money. Ask a question and offer a bounty for the best answers. The userbase then votes to determine which answers receive that bounty.

dapps.name: ChainMonsters
dapps.description: ChainMonsters is a 100% blockchain based monster collectible game. Every action you take, every ChainMonster you catch will be reflected in the game and on blockchain itself.

dapps.name: CryptoCribs
dapps.description: CryptoCribs is a home-sharing platform built for and by the global crypto community. It allows crypto enthusiasts from around the globe to meet like-minded individuals, share their homes and exchange ideas. Travel the world, pay in crypto.

dapps.name: CryptoFighters
dapps.description: CryptoFighters is a game centred around cryptographically unique collectible fighters on the Ethereum blockchain. Collect, battle and level up your fighters to win new fighters!

dapps.name: Crypto High Score
dapps.description: The first high score leaderboard on the blockchain. Pay your way to the top of the immutable, irrefutable global rankings.

dapps.name: Cryptokitties
dapps.description: CryptoKitties is a game centered around breedable, collectible, and oh-so-adorable creatures we call CryptoKitties! Each cat is one-of-a-kind and 100% owned by you; it cannot be replicated, taken away, or destroyed.

dapps.name: CryptoPunks
dapps.description: 10,000 unique collectible characters with proof of ownership stored on the Ethereum blockchain.

dapps.name: Crypto Speech
dapps.description: Decentralized, Twitter-style messages stored for eternity
